		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use ReCon command &quot;oe barracks_assault&quot;&#xD;&#xA;- Go to the Colony Barracks with the debugbook options.&#xD;&#xA;- Get spotted by Krustine, Mistress of Souls (don't get spotted as the Dark Urge character)." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="47" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="If you attacked Ketheric on the rooftop of Moonrise Tower, the Myrkulites in the Colony Barracks will be on high alert. If she spots you, she will assume you are one of the traitors that attacked Ketheric - but you can try to convince her otherwise." />
